   [⊢ ex ≫ ex- ⇒ τx] ...
   [⊢ ey ≫ ey- ⇐ τ] ...
   [([x ≫ x- : τx] ...) ([y ≫ y- : τ] ...) ⊢ body ≫ body- ⇒ τout]
   ------------------
   ;; will this type-eval properly? expand to (typed) app and λ instead?
